data.description: Reduced Price.  Beautiful well kept 3 bedroom home. Large kitchen with an island and lots of cabinets. Fenced in backyard. Home is located close to Rt 33, easy to get to Columbus or Lancaster. Also COTA Park and Ride, shopping and dining is close by. Updates in 2023 include a new shower/tub in the full bath, hot water heater, in 2022 new kitchen appliances, in 2021 AC and Luxury Vinyl flooring. Home has been power washed in 2023.
